name: Demonic Contracts
description:
Alpha edition. These Demonic Contracts warp in and out of our reality and that of the Abyssal Void.

Conversion rate: 13 DC: 1 Soul

The first Demonic Contract minted for the Order of the Dark Wheel. 
Demonic Contracts are part of the currency system for the Order.

To learn more and join the demon hunt, go to:orderofthedarkwheel.com
